        <mxCell id="p3-db" value="Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Maecenas faucibus mollis interdum. Nullam quis risus eget urna ornare.&#xa;&#xa;Duis mollis, est non commodo luctus, nisi erat porttitor ligula, eget lacinia odio sem nec elit.&#xa;&#xa;Section: Significance&#xa;Aenean lacinia bibendum nulla sed consectetur. Cum sociis natoque penatibus et magnis dis parturient montes.&#xa;&#xa;Section: Related&#xa;[Profile: Dilly Knox]&#xa;[Map: Central Europe, 1938]&#xa;[Config: Enigma I Wehrmacht]" style="text;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;fontSize=11;fontColor=#E0E0E0;align=left;verticalAlign=top;whiteSpace=wrap;spacingLeft=4;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1456" y="326" width="432" height="640" as="geometry"/></mxCell>
